divs: Sighting Detailsin nov.1990 i was walking down highway 550 in dwarf kentucky.i heard a wird sound (like a motor like sound).i turned to see if a car or truck was coming,but seen nothing.the sound got louder.i thought that it sounded like it was flying.i looked up behind me.over my left side.i watched a red obejct move over the hill flying low over the tree tops.for the trees was bare i seen it clear.it had looked like the shape of a fish bowl,with a dome top.it was well lite.the bottom was like a up-side down bowl with lights as well.i watched this till it moved over the hill top in front of me,and was gone.i found photos on line that looks like what i seen.
